title: What have you missed most about Dave Chappelle? (19 photos)
text:
“I miss shooting craps with Dave!”– Aundrus 8 
“The unplanned trips to Planned Parenthood.”– Kristen 9 
“Dave’s acerbic wit!”– Patty 10 
“His chalky White lips.”– Nicole 11 
“I miss Dave’s smile & the sound of his voice.”– Andy 12 
“I miss him being as smooth as eggs.”– Aubrey 13 
“Thurgood picking up his prescription .”– Handsome Nick 14 
“I miss the way we used to duck around.”– Ducksworth 15 
“I miss Dave, because of You’ve Got Mail .”– Justine 16 
“I miss Dave’s ability to make anything illegal HILARIOUS.”– Nikki 17 
“I miss Rick James… bitch.”– Dane 18 19 
“I miss my friend’s shitty impressions of Dave’s amazing impressions.”– Dave 
Dave Chappelle is back, and in a big way! Everyone be sure to check out his two new comedy specials TODAY , only on Netflix . 
Tell us what you’ve missed most about Dave in the comments and on social using #davesback . 20
